</title>
<subSubSection id="47E92157BCA69F8C5FA3F12D9A0F3EE5" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" type="description">
<paragraph id="918E88196517F7FBFD357CEA0FADAAFF" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="CB6B09BC0EABD9376D01AD361382C6F7" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis id="29BEA1D46E7F22B46C3DEA37AA5EFB93" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12f) mit Sicherheit einzig 
<emphasis id="B6C68143B8E0AB8C68B34B106DADE606" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
an der 
<normalizedToken id="BE683B7A673890BF7F20B5FFD4EEA17B" originalValue="dunkelgrünen" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">dunkelgruenen</normalizedToken>
Farbe der 
<normalizedToken id="0E6703498CA46C1C7AF951486FE69A3E" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="448CA55E69AC33D3FD80733F0FAD779A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">unterseits oft violett schimmernd und Blattstiele violett</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis id="676BD0D2C4D2CED3E99605E6C5DC79BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
am violetten Sporn und an den braunvioletten 
<normalizedToken id="31B22870CAF9FE74D0B2A0EF72994139" originalValue="Früchten" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Fruechten</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(bei 
<taxonomicName id="CB2A898FDFD71A1A64E27316533455D2" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis id="25D1EF9ED3F23DBDE2CC721FA48CEAF7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="D8BD5DD36ADCF88FFE0C2EF8F5854FDC" originalValue="gelbgrün" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">gelbgruen</normalizedToken>
). - 
<normalizedToken id="1DAA4290F9B23D32196519BA3738320B" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="896CDA632B06512E7B9CF797F1A2591B" originalValue="Früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Frueher</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="329632D0A2C7BD93C109CAEA4502CAB6" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3D1F8F2F51C5CF0B011B73FC89345624" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis id="2CCE1C56C5E907B2FE63DF266DA55F0B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="F3B711E8A93C01893EF6AB7075B55F23" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">20:</emphasis>
Material aus Vorarlberg (Schmidt 1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6D1B9A6CEF50A4501A17D2DA8EB2FEF2" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis id="D8601D87E5B83E1B9F9803D745B0D5E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Standort</emphasis>
. Kollin; 
<normalizedToken id="F309D209799001FCBC5409BFD4E3DA6D" originalValue="ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="83D7CFA88942AC8226B1D838D95D4AAB" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis id="84813281071791F76D168BD003395F2A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12f), aber nur in 
<normalizedToken id="9AA344D8063C2695F7B5F8617B95689C" originalValue="wärmsten" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">waermsten</normalizedToken>
Lagen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3BDD0D9E8938251CEE222BE00CFC124F" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis id="AC4014BA0E1BD487B890A2B8540C6338" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="0173A81F61C991C843AFC8DD5F82BF90" originalValue="Südosteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Suedosteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="78456F1D392FAEBB4589C9262FF19D60" originalValue="Nordwestwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Nordwestwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis in die Nordalpen. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="B58CA3966C55EBD080C99AAD78D6D68B" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="FE77DAE6747F4E0F6B5FB22FDDD1832E" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis id="0FD4E2B1FBE9D770AC63BBBBA8260F5D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12f), aber besonders im 
<normalizedToken id="FED0D7F0E2C0B3B69C99472799DCCF9A" originalValue="südlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">suedlichen</normalizedToken>
Teil; im Rheintal 
<normalizedToken id="794048E11A6CC042541E60191512AF8B" originalValue="aufwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">aufwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Chur.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CE80E4C11D53F18DD701A0924772B6D8" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
<emphasis id="6563F6679691FD3CA1CD6B556AC40821" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">
Bemerkungen. 
<taxonomicName id="A6DBA92D0268DBFF2E63A19E7510AE82" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scotophylla">V. scotophylla</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
ist nur wenig verschieden von 
<taxonomicName id="F03AE1C4AD592AAF089A55E7C3E3061B" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alba">
<emphasis id="D34346D67D242E60B172B3CE6786CC80" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. alba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und hat auch fast die gleiche Verbreitung. Vielleicht ist das charakteristische Farbmerkmal der 
<normalizedToken id="C56CEF925C2A434BDEF39349B458EE15" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
und des Sporns auf Introgression von 
<taxonomicName id="62FC1094F4E7CAD79DE9F3BEA988F5B8" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="744" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirta">
<emphasis id="95F9E9B7A88041237A21E9AF8DE79C39" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">V. hirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12b) 
<normalizedToken id="43FC29C250A1FEC618DB600DDC905580" originalValue="zurückzuführen" pageId="null" pageNumber="744">zurueckzufuehren</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
